He's not wrong, though. The mountains would look really cool with some snow on them. I'm guessing that's more of a texture/EVA type fix.

Snowy Mountain used to have snow on the plateau and peak. If it doesn't now, that's a change of the terrain map and nothing to do with KerbinSide.

So I installed Kerbinside... got it all. Launched a plane, really laggy, set kerbal to high priority in task manager,
